<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Digitize This Photo - Professional Photo Scanning</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .section { padding: 2rem; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 3rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .hero h2 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .hero-subtitle { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #555; }
    .hero-image-container { display: block; margin: 0 auto 2rem auto; max-width: 600px; }
    .hero img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; }
    .hero-text { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero-secondary-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 2rem; text-align: left; }
    .secondary-photo-holder { flex: 1 1 350px; text-align: center; }
    .secondary-text-holder { flex: 2 1 400px; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #0056b3; color: #fff; padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .problem-solution, .pricing-tiers, .how-steps, .gallery, .testimonials { display: flex; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .pricing-card, .how-step, .testimonial, .problem, .solution { flex: 1 1 300px; background: #fff; padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; }
    .badge-popular { background: #e67e22; color: #fff; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; border-radius: 3px; vertical-align: middle; }
    .before-after { flex: 1 1 300px; text-align: center; background: #f9f9f9; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #eee; }
    .before-after img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cta-multi { text-align: center; background: #eef2f7; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; }
    .cta-phone { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #0056b3; margin: 0.5rem 0; }
    .faq-item { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .contact-details { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; }
    footer { background: #333; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    a { color: #0056b3; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <div class="hero">
    <h2>Professional Photo Scanning for Families & Generations</h2>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Keep your family story safe, easy to share, and ready for the next generation.</p>

    <div class="hero-image-container">
      <img src="hero-david.jpg" alt="Digitize This Photo Main Heading Image">
    </div>
    
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-secondary-row">
        <div class="secondary-photo-holder">
          <img src="david-scanning.jpg" alt="David scanning photos" style="display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;">
        </div>
        <div class="secondary-text-holder">
          <p>
            We gently digitize your printed photos and return them as simple digital folders you and your family
            can enjoy on phones, tablets, and TVs—without boxes and clutter.
          </p>
          <a class="cta-btn" href="#contact">Get a Free Quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PROBLEM / SOLUTION -->
  <div class="section" id="problem">
    <h2>Your Memories Are Fading...</h2>
    <div class="problem-solution">
      <div class="problem">
        <h3>The Problem</h3>
        <p>Photos yellowing, colours fading, albums sitting in basements—your family history is slowly disappearing.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Prints damaged by time, sunlight, and handling.</li>
          <li>Loose photos scattered across boxes and drawers.</li>
          <li>Old CDs, DVDs, or hard drives you no longer trust.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="solution">
        <h3>We Make It Simple</h3>
        <p>Our service is designed to be easy, safe, and worry‑free.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Free consultation before you decide.</li>
          <li>Secure handling of your photos from start to finish.</li>
          <li>Fast turnaround so you can share quickly.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- PRICING TIERS -->
  <div class="section" id="pricing">
    <h2>Simple, Clear Pricing</h2>
    <div class="pricing-tiers">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Tier 1: BASIC</h3>
        <p><strong>$0.39 per photo</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Standard‑quality scans for everyday prints up to 8×10 inches.</li>
          <li>Basic colour and contrast adjustment.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Tier 2: PREMIUM <span class="badge-popular">Popular</span></h3>
        <p><strong>$0.65 per photo</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Higher‑resolution scans for important photos.</li>
          <li>More careful adjustment of colour and brightness.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Tier 3: LEGACY</h3>
        <p><strong>$1.25 per photo</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Highest‑quality scans and extra attention to detail.</li>
          <li>Best option if you plan to make books or large prints.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CONTACT INFO -->
  <div class="section" id="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <div class="contact-details">
      <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 416‑479‑9549</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@digitizethisphoto.com">info@digitizethisphoto.com</a></p>
      <p><strong>Location:</strong> Toronto, Ontario</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    Digitize This Photo © 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Preserving your past so your family can enjoy it in the future.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
